into the West End Pavilion Hospital.

527
00:37:40,302 --> 00:37:43,138
The boy was unconscious
from severe head injuries.

528
00:37:43,222 --> 00:37:44,890
She said he fell.

529
00:37:44,973 --> 00:37:46,433
The doctor says...

530
00:37:46,767 --> 00:37:50,562
...the head wounds were too symmetrical
to be the result of a fall.

531
00:37:50,979 --> 00:37:52,481
He told me...

532
00:37:52,648 --> 00:37:56,652
...he was treating a child whose mother
had crushed his head in a vise.

533
00:37:58,612 --> 00:38:01,073
