538
00:38:13,794 --> 00:38:17,714
Look, how many child abuse cases
does this office handle in a year?

539
00:38:17,840 --> 00:38:19,091
Over a thousand.

540
00:38:19,174 --> 00:38:21,176
Every one of them terrible.

541
00:38:21,802 --> 00:38:23,679
Every one of them heartbreaking.

542
00:38:23,762 --> 00:38:27,057
But I can't stop everything else
to take care of one case.

543
00:38:27,140 --> 00:38:30,269
