I fucked some fat-cat friend of Raymond's.

549
00:38:53,792 --> 00:38:55,252
Look, it's late...

550
00:38:58,338 --> 00:39:00,841
Come on, I'll drive you to your ferry.

551
00:39:04,219 --> 00:39:06,471
This is not the way to the ferry.

552
00:39:06,889 --> 00:39:08,724
I want you to meet somebody.

553
00:39:08,807 --> 00:39:11,018
Wendell, this is Rusty Sabich.

554
00:39:13,812 --> 00:39:16,523
He's a very important man in our office.

555
00:39:16,773 --> 00:39:19,693
He's going to help me
when we go to court.

556
00:39:20,694 --> 00:39:23,030
Remember what I told you about court?

557
00:39:23,322 --> 00:39:24,406
Yeah.

558
00:39:25,157 --> 00:39:26,658
Now, tell me.

559
00:39:27,743 --> 00:39:30,037
There's a judge and some nice people.

560
00:39:30,120 --> 00:39:31,997
They're called a jury.

561
00:39:32,414 --> 00:39:34,791
