664
00:48:51,265 --> 00:48:55,185
I'm at the North Branch before 5:00,
going through the microfilm.

665
00:48:55,811 --> 00:48:58,188
All of this hits by 6:00, 6:30.

666
00:48:59,064 --> 00:49:01,984
Look what I picked up
while I was out there.

667
00:49:02,192 --> 00:49:04,403
The case number matches
the complaint number...

668
00:49:04,486 --> 00:49:06,905
...that was missing
when you saw Kenneally.

669
00:49:06,989 --> 00:49:08,991
Five years ago. Bingo.

670
00:49:09,616 --> 00:49:12,661
And look who's listed
as Leon's probation officer.

671
00:49:15,164 --> 00:49:16,248
"Carolyn Polhemus."

672
00:49:16,331 --> 00:49:18,333
Wait. Here's the best.

673
00:49:19,293 --> 00:49:22,212
Who do you think was the deputy
handling the case?

674
00:49:24,840 --> 00:49:26,175
Tommy Molto.

675
00:49:26,717 --> 00:49:30,929
You keep this because I don't know
what the fuck is happening with me.

676
00:49:37,936 --> 00:49:39,354
Tommy Molto.

677
00:49:39,980 --> 00:49:43,901
Tommy Molto once worked here,
but we think he might be dead.

678
00:49:44,860 --> 00:49:46,445
Raymond's inside.

679
00:49:46,528 --> 00:49:48,363
We've been waiting for you.

680
00:49:56,622 --> 00:49:57,664
Rusty.

681
00:49:59,291 --> 00:50:00,959
Molto and Delay...

682
00:50:02,711 --> 00:50:05,714
...have questions about
the Polhemus investigation.

683
00:50:06,548 --> 00:50:08,884
This should not be handled this way.

684
00:50:09,301 --> 00:50:11,470
You should speak with Rusty alone.

685
00:50:12,638 --> 00:50:13,472
What's this about?

686
00:50:13,555 --> 00:50:16,850
You were at Carolyn's apartment
the night she was killed.

687
00:50:16,975 --> 00:50:18,227
Bullshit.

688
00:50:24,191 --> 00:50:26,401
What was it, a Tuesday night?

689
00:50:28,737 --> 00:50:31,573
Barbara was at the university.
I was babysitting.

690
00:50:31,657 --> 00:50:33,784
Keep your fucking mouth shut.

691
00:50:33,909 --> 00:50:36,078
We got the fingerprint results...

692
00:50:36,161 --> 00:50:38,705
...the ones that you could never remember
to ask for.

693
00:50:38,789 --> 00:50:41,291
They're your prints all over the bar glass.

694
00:50:41,375 --> 00:50:43,377
Yours, Rozat K. Sabich.

695
00:50:44,127 --> 00:50:46,922
